MSNSTR:UNICAS:USA03OB:INTRO1
"Yemen, Sanaa
\nOperation: Beehive"
END

MSNSTR:UNICAS:USA03OB:INTRO2
"General! We failed to hold peace in the city
\nWe thought that we had destroyed the GLA
\nbut they are rising again!"
END

MSNSTR:UNICAS:USA03OB:BRIEFING1
"Objective one:
\nDestroy the GLA base in the north"
END

MSNSTR:UNICAS:USA03OB:BRIEFING2
"Objective two:
\nDestroy the rest of the GLA in this area"
END
